[75.809506, "o", "Scheduled Meeting: 2024-01-17 11:00:00 to 2024-01-17 12:00:00\r\nDay of week: Wednesday\r\n\r\nAlice constraints:\r\n  - Time window (9 AM - 2 PM): True ✓\r\n  - Existing meetings on Jan 17: 10-11 AM, 1-2 PM\r\n  - No conflict: ✓ (11 AM - 12 PM is free)\r\n"]
